        "content": "<p data-pid=\"ev9AMtYB\"><b>判断一个数是否为2的幂次方</b></p><p data-pid=\"3Lw13xmC\">看到这个问题，99%的人第一反应是写个循环，不断除以2。但真正的高手，只需要一行代码：</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><img src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-9dd1b8aec6b98a236ff1db209652fb09_1440w.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"918\" data-rawheight=\"194\" data-size=\"normal\" data-caption=\"\" data-original-token=\"v2-9dd1b8aec6b98a236ff1db209652fb09\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-54d2aa53ddc8a7c67f7d189725d10f92_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"918\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-9dd1b8aec6b98a236ff1db209652fb09_r.jpg\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"pQ58VbXf\">传统方法代码</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><img src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-38c1aeb16f17aae9616721b81c9e9eb9_1440w.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"804\" data-rawheight=\"440\" data-size=\"normal\" data-caption=\"\" data-original-token=\"v2-38c1aeb16f17aae9616721b81c9e9eb9\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-c17d1a791e0bfc848b34edb6db9b1dae_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"804\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-38c1aeb16f17aae9616721b81c9e9eb9_r.jpg\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"VWjdZ9Bw\"><b>为什么这么神奇？</b></p><p data-pid=\"FHqDbiv7\">这背后利用了一个数学规律：2的幂次方在二进制中只有一个1位。</p><p data-pid=\"fZ3EgpDq\">比如：</p><ul><li data-pid=\"I8SmCda4\">8 = <code>1000</code></li><li data-pid=\"VAL47Ef4\">16 = <code>10000</code></li><li data-pid=\"nBUIBIv9\">1024 = <code>10000000000</code> </li></ul><p data-pid=\"Ai-WNfpT\">当你给它减1时，魔法发生了：</p><ul><li data-pid=\"KGymtonu\">8-1 = 7 = <code>0111</code> </li><li data-pid=\"URkGN-8Q\">16-1 = 15 = <code>01111</code></li></ul><p data-pid=\"WMCkuDWd\">原来的那个1变成0，后面全变成1！</p><p data-pid=\"pDoAPyOt\">用位与运算<code>&amp;</code>一算：<code>1000 &amp; 0111 = 0000</code>，直接归零！</p><p data-pid=\"r-drBylC\">而不是2的幂次方的数呢？比如6：</p><ul><li data-pid=\"VDMBHsqJ\">6 = <code>110</code></li><li data-pid=\"Yd8AA9vF\">5 = <code>101</code></li><li data-pid=\"lxmE1PcA\">6 &amp; 5 = <code>100</code> ≠ 0</li></ul><p data-pid=\"BXaJNEzX\"><b>复杂度分析</b></p><p data-pid=\"2i6GiwnK\">无论输入多大的数，这个算法都只做一次减法和一次位运算，严格的O(1)时间复杂度。</p><p data-pid=\"lScVo4LP\">传统的循环方法是O(log n)，当数字很大时，比如2^63，传统方法要循环63次，而这个算法依然只需要一步。</p><p data-pid=\"b3km0J1x\"><b>实际效果测试</b></p><div class=\"highlight\"><pre><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"kn\">import</span> <span class=\"nn\">time</span>\n\n\n<span class=\"k\">def</span> <span class=\"nf\">is_power_of_two</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">n</span><span class=\"p\">):</span>\n    <span class=\"k\">return</span> <span class=\"n\">n</span> <span class=\"o\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"mi\">0</span> <span class=\"ow\">and</span> <span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">n</span> <span class=\"o\">&amp;</span> <span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">n</span> <span class=\"o\">-</span> <span class=\"mi\">1</span><span class=\"p\">))</span> <span class=\"o\">==</span> <span class=\"mi\">0</span>\n\n\n<span class=\"k\">def</span> <span class=\"nf\">is_power_of_two_traditional</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">n</span><span class=\"p\">):</span>\n    <span class=\"k\">if</span> <span class=\"n\">n</span> <span class=\"o\">&lt;=</span> <span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"p\">:</span>\n        <span class=\"k\">return</span> <span class=\"bp\">False</span>\n    <span class=\"k\">while</span> <span class=\"n\">n</span> <span class=\"o\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"mi\">1</span><span class=\"p\">:</span>\n        <span class=\"k\">if</span> <span class=\"n\">n</span> <span class=\"o\">%</span> <span class=\"mi\">2</span> <span class=\"o\">!=</span> <span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"p\">:</span>\n            <span class=\"k\">return</span> <span class=\"bp\">False</span>\n        <span class=\"n\">n</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">n</span> <span class=\"o\">//</span> <span class=\"mi\">2</span>\n    <span class=\"k\">return</span> <span class=\"bp\">True</span>\n\n<span class=\"k\">if</span> <span class=\"vm\">__name__</span> <span class=\"o\">==</span> <span class=\"s1\">&#39;__main__&#39;</span><span class=\"p\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"n\">num</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"mi\">2</span> <span class=\"o\">**</span> <span class=\"mi\">2000</span>\n    <span class=\"k\">print</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">num</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n    <span class=\"n\">start_at</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">time</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">time</span><span class=\"p\">()</span>\n    <span class=\"k\">print</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">is_power_of_two</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">num</span><span class=\"p\">))</span>\n    <span class=\"k\">print</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">f</span><span class=\"s2\">&#34;take: {time.time() - start_at}&#34;</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n\n    <span class=\"n\">start_at</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">time</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">time</span><span class=\"p\">()</span>\n    <span class=\"k\">print</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">is_power_of_two_traditional</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">num</span><span class=\"p\">))</span>\n    <span class=\"k\">print</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">f</span><span class=\"s2\">&#34;take: {time.time() - start_at}&#34;</span><span class=\"p\">)</span></code></pre></div><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br/></p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-a9dc8f5c3d221b4caaf27af8a7d1ac15_1440w.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"1212\" data-rawheight=\"1316\" data-size=\"normal\" data-caption=\"\" data-original-token=\"v2-a9dc8f5c3d221b4caaf27af8a7d1ac15\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-71118138b911cb8ede0daa2fc9925492_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1212\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-a9dc8f5c3d221b4caaf27af8a7d1ac15_r.jpg\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"6Hkp0QlK\">在我机器上测试，面对2 ** 200这个数：</p><ul><li data-pid=\"g1dsN2RL\">此方法：9.5367431640625e-07 秒</li><li data-pid=\"G4st1EKx\">传统算法：0.0003247261047363281 秒</li></ul><figure data-size=\"normal\"><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-e4f575fd96edf0db1e71d8872fbda4cc_1440w.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"1560\" data-rawheight=\"870\" data-size=\"normal\" data-caption=\"\" data-original-token=\"v2-e4f575fd96edf0db1e71d8872fbda4cc\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-9cf55c3551d8215e666515e11e68e621_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1560\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-e4f575fd96edf0db1e71d8872fbda4cc_r.jpg\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"8cQCatx4\">性能提升百倍！</p><p data-pid=\"J0ZUWjxk\">这就是位运算的牛逼之处。</p>",
